about.summary: Local SFTP server fixture plugin for pytest

name: pytest-sftpserver
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "pytest-sftpserver" %}
{% set version = "1.1.2" %}
{% set sha256 = "b84fee01a9c0137e32290497851cbfb2c1553be587907d609568dadc8a3d16ed" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python
    - paramiko
    - six

test:
  imports:
    - pytest_sftpserver

about:
  home: https://github.com/ulope/pytest-sftpserver
  license: MIT
  summary: Local SFTP server fixture plugin for pytest

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - vamega
